,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:29:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">點解全世界大部分嘅黑科技都係美國發明嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n中國唔係好撚巴閉㗎咩</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"42f1099b1a681c82ff138d9acd16abaefa019ec4","tid":674131,"uid":26506,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"quote":{"pid":"f26c13d2f63f353dbd7c1cdc3bcd5fe2446acc91","tid":674131,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:15:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/100088/page/1?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/100088/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thenewslens.com/article/60336\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewslens.com%2Farticle%2F60336&d=12lp2R5cnTfP%2BQom2E5C5S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3ff6c24d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thenewslens.com/article/60336</a> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.thenewslens.com/2017/1/80ts5h4vpchkqq8nbap0qqmwa8cql2.png?fitcroph600q100w1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.thenewslens.com%2F2017%2F1%2F80ts5h4vpchkqq8nbap0qqmwa8cql2.png%3Ffitcroph600q100w1000&h=5b4369a9&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你為什麼需要這則新聞 <br />\n<br />\n「這是高壓物理的終極目標。」席維拉說：「這是有史以來第1個金屬氫樣本，當你看著它，你看的是以前從未存在過的物質。」 <br />\n<br />\n（中央社） <br />\n美國科學家將氫充分壓縮，首度成功使其轉變成為金屬，創造出1種全新的物質，可望在室溫中作為高效率電導體，對超導體的發展具有極高價值。 <br />\n<br />\n路透社和「紐約時報」（NYT）報導，今天發表於「科學」（Science）期刊的這項發現，首度證實物理學家杭亭頓（Hillard Bell Huntington）和魏格納（Eugene Wigner）1935年提出的理論，即將一般為氣體的氫暴露於極高壓環境下，就可能使其成為金屬狀態。 <br />\n<br />\n多個研究團隊致力研發「金屬氫」，由於金屬氫可能成為導電效率極高的「超導體」，因此相當珍貴。現階段，比如那些用在核磁共振攝影（MRI）的超導體，必須使用液態氦冷卻，讓它們維持在極低溫度，代價高昂。 <br />\n<br />\n研究執筆人之一、哈佛（Harvard）物理學家席維拉（Isaac Silvera）在聲明中說：「這是高壓物理的終極目標。」 <br />\n<br />\n席維拉說：「這是有史以來第1個金屬氫樣本，當你看著它，你看的是以前從未存在過的物質。」 <br />\n<br />\n伊利諾大學香檳校區（University of Illinois at Urbana-Champaign）物理教授瑟培利（David Ceperley）說，這項發現若經證實，將為數十年來探索如何取得金屬氫的研究畫下句點，也會讓人們更加了解這種宇宙中最常見的元素。瑟培利並未參與這項研究。 <br />\n<br />\n席維拉和同僚狄亞斯（Ranga Dias）將微小的氫樣本以每6.5平方公分3250萬公斤的壓力進行壓縮，強度超過地球中心壓力。也已逼近合成鑽石強度崩潰邊緣。 <br />\n<br />\n關鍵問題是，經過壓縮的氫能否在室溫下維持金屬屬性，這會使其成為非常有用的超導體。 <br />\n<br />\n瑟培利和席維拉都對此表示樂觀，不過仍待更多研究證實。 <br />\n<br />\n刊登在「科學」的研究原文：Observation of the Wigner-Huntington transition to metallic hydrogen <br />\n<br />\n自由報導，研究證實1935年物理學家杭亭頓（Hillard Bell Huntington）、魏格納（Eugene Wigner）的理論預測，即氫氣在高壓下會變相成為金屬氫。美國康乃爾大學物理學家艾許克洛夫特（Neil Ashcroft）認為，金屬氫在攝氏17度可能也是超導體，遠高於已知的超導體材料。 <br />\n<br />\n當前許多頂尖研究團隊都致力研究取得金屬氫，去年一月英國愛丁堡大學也在「自然（Nature）」期刊刊出金屬氫可行性的研究。超導體具零電阻和抗磁性兩個重要特性，目前超導材料的最高溫紀錄為2015年德國普朗克研究所發表的「硫化氫」的零下70度。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:31:13.000Z","msg":"[wow]"},{"pid":"9aaa2e6732b90e5dc14312c16e33582ac4e09069","tid":674131,"uid":33213,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e6ffadd8be49dd7933751a43136c8792353fd8b2","tid":674131,"uid":147721,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"0a8be02622460e2e03181c306ae3b47c9183397b","tid":674131,"uid":83623,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"a420baa4a34655cb4fac4af3e47db85ea000839d","tid":674131,"uid":67903,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:38:03.000Z","msg":"將微小的氫樣本以每6.5平方公分3250萬公斤的壓力進行壓縮，強度超過地球中心壓力。<br />\n<br />\n個實驗室其實點樣控制個壓力施係氫身上而唔會外泄到實驗室外???"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T12:44:57.000Z","msg":"用兩粒鑽石壓埋一齊，只係好短時間係金屬<br />\n<img src=\"http://www.sciencemag.org/sites/default/files/styles/inline__699w__no_aspect/public/metallic_hydrogen_1280.jpg?itok=WjcXtCMc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencemag.org%2Fsites%2Fdefault%2Ffiles%2Fstyles%2Finline__699w__no_aspect%2Fpublic%2Fmetallic_hydrogen_1280.jpg%3Fitok%3DWjcXtCMc&h=93de54fe&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T13:29:00.000Z","msg":"有paper預測過金屬氫係常溫常壓個時係meta stable"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:37:01.000Z","msg":"除非有新方法唔使用diamond anvil都整到咁大pressure<br />\n唔係嘅話就算係metastable都係得個噏字"},{"pid":"00c161d5a054ec1ec83852cd14da2d984b1b365f","tid":674131,"uid":63119,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:39:52.000Z","msg":"美國研究強國山寨<br />\n可以節省資源做其他野<br />\n強國又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67031e4daed4b6f48b25e4f02565021b7ac3db68","tid":674131,"uid":38744,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:43:04.000Z","msg":"係就真係人類嘅大進步"},{"pid":"f2acb60e074f79d8f5b08bb4f28f4685a7d2451d","tid":674131,"uid":875,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:44:09.000Z","msg":"諗起Tony stark<br />\n<br />\n一日之間由研究到制成new element<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 當要有少少父幹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0999f80857c5c9aac2fec0a4a9ecd197e588ec15","tid":674131,"uid":30791,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:47:13.000Z","msg":"維持高壓易過維持低溫? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e27ec05c73df581c16d416fa93d0a5fdeb08ce3","tid":674131,"uid":2389,"like":8,"dislike":3,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T14:47:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8f461f672c35986cc01569ef5a0ce01b7a7f89bb","tid":674131,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T15:21:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://arxiv.org/abs/1705.04900\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Farxiv.org%2Fabs%2F1705.04900&d=12lp2R5cnTfP%2BQom2E5C5S7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=3cf292b8\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/abs/1705.04900</a><br />\n<br />\n同埋metastable只限&gt;200GPa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果個theory冇錯<br />\n咁都真係幾難有practical application<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}